FortyTwo BBS @VERSION@ - pre-alpha
for x86_64 glibc-based Linux systems.
Tested on Ubuntu 25.10 with rootless
Podman. Debian container support is
planned; BSD testing will follow later.
Open-source Bulletin Board System with
Fidonet mailer, tosser, TIC processing,
message areas, Doors and file utilities.
Local test access is available by Telnet
and restricted SSH. Based on MBSE BBS.
Released under GNU GPL version 2.
Project & Source:
https://github.com/Juergen-Coding/FortyTwoBBS
Support:
